03:16.654 --> 03:19.573
- This is gonna be
the best year ever.

03:19.574 --> 03:20.782
- Wuh-whoa!

03:22.619 --> 03:24.620
- You better hide it
before Miss Rood sees.

03:24.621 --> 03:25.996
- Ah, come on.

03:25.997 --> 03:27.998
- Charley, you can't get
expelled on the first day.

03:27.999 --> 03:29.583
- You can't worry
on the first day!

03:29.584 --> 03:31.335
♪ ♪

03:31.336 --> 03:32.544
- So what'd you bring us?

03:32.545 --> 03:34.171
- Just some downers I stole
from my mom.

03:34.172 --> 03:36.298
- Well, I got chocolate
in Geneva.

03:36.299 --> 03:37.925
- You guys hear about
Annabelle?

03:37.926 --> 03:39.843
She's been hooking up
with two different boys

03:39.844 --> 03:40.928
from Langley College.

03:40.929 --> 03:42.262
- What?
- Such a whore.

03:42.263 --> 03:43.931
- Jealous?
