03:53.650 --> 03:55.150
Hey, Lucy, what about you
and Jason?

03:55.151 --> 03:56.151
- I broke up with him.

03:56.152 --> 03:57.152
- Yeah, on Facebook.

03:57.153 --> 03:58.487
How cold is that?

03:58.488 --> 04:00.322
- What about you, Becca?

04:00.323 --> 04:01.323
- I don't know.

04:01.324 --> 04:03.492
