wants to do it.

10:22.371 --> 10:25.206
- I used to study Greek
and Latin.

10:25.207 --> 10:28.710
I was very serious,
even though I was a girl.

10:28.711 --> 10:34.049
Then other things intervened.

10:37.136 --> 10:39.512
- Okay, well, um...

10:39.513 --> 10:42.390
I'm late for my class, so...

