12:27.913 --> 12:29.497
I'm just gonna go say hi.

12:32.084 --> 12:33.835
Hey.

12:33.836 --> 12:35.378
What are you reading?

12:35.379 --> 12:37.088
- It's a book I found
in the library.

12:37.089 --> 12:38.757
Sit down.

12:38.758 --> 12:40.800
- What's it called?

12:40.801 --> 12:42.886
- It's called...

12:42.887 --> 12:46.014
- ♪ Slow emotion ♪

13:24.303 --> 13:32.310
