and creepy.

13:57.920 --> 14:00.463
- She has trouble sleeping.
So what?

14:00.464 --> 14:03.716
- You don't think
it's kind of strange?

14:03.717 --> 14:05.927
- She has issues.

14:05.928 --> 14:08.763
Stuff with her family.

14:08.764 --> 14:10.765
She's a nice person
if you give her a chance.

14:19.608 --> 14:27.615
♪ ♪

14:50.472 --> 14:51.681
- I'm sorry to interrupt.

14:51.682 --> 14:54.350
I usually use this room.

14:55.978 --> 14:57.520
I didn't know
you played the piano.

14:57.521 --> 15:00.565
- I hardly ever play anymore.

15:00.566 --> 15:02.066
- You play so well.

15:02.067 --> 15:04.527
How do you do that
without looking at the music?

15:04.528 --> 15:07.614
- My father was a musician.

15:07.615 --> 15:11.200
I inherited everything
from him,

15:11.201 --> 15:14.537
