17:09.611 --> 17:12.113
- That lavender bath oil
feels so good.

17:12.114 --> 17:13.614
- I know.
I can smell it from here.

17:13.615 --> 17:15.032
- What are you reading?
- CarmiIIa.

17:15.034 --> 17:16.451
It's for Mr. Davies' class.

17:16.452 --> 17:17.452
- What's it about?

17:19.454 --> 17:21.539
- Hey.

17:21.540 --> 17:24.791
- You know,
it's Gothic fiction.

17:24.792 --> 17:26.127
- You're burning red.

17:26.127 --> 17:28.296
How do you stand such hot water
on your skin?

17:28.297 --> 17:30.339
- We always take hot baths
