- So I've brought us
a list of verbs to conjugate.

17:35.596 --> 17:39.432
Let's start with baden,
to bathe.

17:39.433 --> 17:40.475
- Baden.

17:40.476 --> 17:41.476
- Mm-hmm.

17:41.477 --> 17:45.480
Beginnen.

17:53.280 --> 17:54.739
- Beginnen.

17:54.740 --> 17:57.658
I'll show you how far I got.

